                    | Saturday: #{globals.ipf.date.saturday.hours.start} - #{globals.ipf.date.saturday.hours.stop}
                    br
                    | Sunday: #{globals.ipf.date.sunday.hours.start} - #{globals.ipf.date.sunday.hours.stop}


            dt When is the parade?
            dd The parade occurs on Saturday at #{globals.events.parade.time}.

            dt Are Pets Allowed?
            dd No. Per City of Atlanta Ordinance, pets are not allowed at Festivals, "unless part of a planned festival program or assisting persons with disabilities". This prohibition includes "dogs, cats, snakes, birds, pigs, etc.", and applies whether or not the pet is leashed. As the ordinance says, this is for the pet's protection as well as for the protection of festival patrons. Thanks!!
        
        h2 Tour of Homes Tickets 
        
        dl.FaqList
            dt How much do Tour of Homes Tickets Cost?
            dd Tour of Homes tickets are $#{globals.tour.cost.advance} in advance and $#{globals.tour.cost.door} starting Friday, #{globals.ipf.date.friday.date} (online sales incur a small additional ticket service fee).

            dt Can I use my digital ticket to get into a home on the Tour of Homes?
            dd Yes. You must first install the Eventeny app on your mobile device. When you arrive at the home on Tour, show the volunteer your device with the QR code visible and your digital ticket will be scanned.

            dt Are there group ticket rates?
            dd Yes, group discounts are available for groups of 10 or more.
        
        h2 Markets
        
        dl.FaqList
