        h2 Food 
        
        dl.FaqList
            dt What food is available at the festival?
            dd Pizza, barbecue, gyros, sandwiches, and, of course, funnel cakes and other street festival staples. Vegetarian, Vegan, and Gluten-Free options will also be available.  Local restaurants will also be open for business.


        h2 Sponsors
        
        dl.FaqList
            dt What levels of sponsorships does the festival offer?
            dd There are several levels of sponsorships available to businesses of all sizes, including Gold and Silver levels as well as Friends of Festival designations.

            dt How do I learn more about sponsorships?
            dd Go to the <a href="/contact-us">Contact Us page</a> and send an e-mail request to Festival Sponsorships.


